                           int amount)
                    throws ClientException
        Decrease the amount of the resource by the specified amount.

        amount: - int, The amount of the resource to remove from the bank
        Throws:
        ClientException - if this function runs and dies when it shouldn't

      • endTurn

        public void endTurn()
             throws ClientException
        Switches to the next player; player 0 if currently on player 3
        Throws:
        ClientException
        Precondition
        None
        Postcondition
        Calls Player.endTurn(), updates the version and the if there is one. Updates the turn tracker with the status. Updates the winner if the player has won.
